AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000179> "BFO OWL specification label"@en)

# Annotation Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000180> (BFO CLIF specification label)

