AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000111> "The concise, meaningful, and human-friendly name for a class or property preferred by the ontology developers. (US-English)"@en)
