# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002090> (immediately precedes)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002090> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7073-9172>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000118> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002090> "ends_at_start_of")
