AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002428> "c involved in regulation of p if c is involved in some p' and p' regulates some p")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002428> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6601-2165>)
