SubObjectPropertyOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002428> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002431>)

# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002429> (involved in positive regulation of)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002429> "c involved in regulation of p if c is involved in some p' and p' positively regulates some p")
