AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002578> "p directly regulates q iff p is immediately causally upstream of q and p regulates q.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002578> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6601-2165>)
