# Object Property: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002584> (has part structure that is capable of)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000112> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002584> "gland SubClassOf 'has part structure that is capable of' some 'secretion by cell'")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002584> "s 'has part structure that is capable of' p if and only if there exists some part x such that s 'has part' x and x 'capable of' p")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002584> <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6601-2165>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002584> "has part structure that is capable of")
